@undertheteacup (cont) Pressure? Stress? Tension? Suspicion?

I think I like Tension, because it can be used to describe the tone of the scene AND the mood of the characters.

So Genre moves from Murder Mystery to Slice of Life, and Tension slides from 0 (chill) to 6 (breaking point).

